{"tid":962691,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱行過天悅廣場　法國啲卡game毒撚真係人生既失敗者","createTime":"2018-12-31T05:20:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-31T14:58:24.000Z","uid":8307,"like":122,"dislike":143,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"0df58421556aba14d80241fa7cf50db1cd8f3070","tid":962691,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T05:20:09.000Z","msg":"差唔多個個都已經三十幾歲<br />\n仲未有份穩定既工,日日得閒行黎炒卡打卡<br />\n唔係看更就係工廠工人,離唔開都係啲散工仔<br />\n人工唔知一個月有冇一皮<br />\n睇佢地個死毒樣都知冇個有女,雞都唔知敢唔敢叫<br />\n成份雞碎咁多既糧都用哂去玩呢啲玩具到<br />\n講下笑問下佢地銀行戶口有幾錢?即刻閪哂面<br />\n得返卡鋪係佢地可以拎到成就感同自信既地方<br />\n其實唔只遊戲王，BS同精靈寶可夢卡驚都一堆咁既人<br />\n玩魔法風雲會個啲就高汁少少"},{"pid":"7c35f132fa4a47d9aa92661a21ac0ddb59552b2c","tid":962691,"uid":147871,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T05:31:02.000Z","msg":"Fgo?"},{"pid":"9c2974aff869ced419ce1aef84986e8cd53e3210","tid":962691,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T05:31:46.000Z","msg":"55"},{"pid":"c812822e04e07d4e212c4b10674ab1e2b70b8db0","tid":962691,"uid":8307,"like":11,"dislike":17,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"7c35f132fa4a47d9aa92661a21ac0ddb59552b2c","tid":962691,"uid":147871,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T05:31:02.000Z","msg":"Fgo?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T05:32:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4OVkDkr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4OVkDkr.jpg&h=7a98fb37&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fdfcb61150c8f2b469cea230039e3ef4f53108b2","tid":962691,"uid":103948,"like":61,"dislike":1,"score":60,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T05:35:29.000Z","msg":"乜撚野精靈寶可夢"},{"pid":"bb689254fd2efbe170bfb8ebeea1c6332dc7f786","tid":962691,"uid":8307,"like":3,"dislike":121,"score":-118,"quote":{"pid":"fdfcb61150c8f2b469cea230039e3ef4f53108b2","tid":962691,"uid":103948,"like":61,"dislike":1,"score":60,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T05:35:29.000Z","msg":"乜撚野精靈寶可夢"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T05:36:14.000